To play MPSOD, follow these instructions:1. Make a copy of the Wolfenstein 3D application and keep it in your Wolfenstein 3D folder. 2. Open the copy of the Wolfenstein 3D application with ResEdit.3. Find the "csnd" picker and open it. Delete the resource with ID number 166.4. Open the "MPSOD Resources" ResEdit file supplied with MPSOD.5. Select all the pickers in this file, copy them, then paste them into the copy of Wolfenstein 3D. Answer "yes" when asked if you wish to replace resources with the same ID number.6. Save changes and quit ResEdit.7. Put the MPSOD level file in the Levels folder in your Wolfenstein 3D folder.8. Launch the copy of Wolfenstein 3D and select the MPSOD scenario.